title: Keweenaw National Historical Park: Eating & Sleeping
body: Explore This Park    Plan Your Visit     Eating & Sleeping             Eating & Sleeping        Catch a beautiful sunset on the Keweenaw. NPS, Valerie Newman           Lodging The Keweenaw has a variety of lodging and camping opportunities. For a list of options please visit the Keweenaw Convention and Visitor's Bureau website or call 906-337-4579.        There are many places to eat across the Keweenaw. NPS, Valerie Newman  Eating Eating establishments abound the Keweenaw. You'll find something for everyone and every budget. A sizable list can be found by visiting the Keweenaw Convention and Visitors Bureau restaurants page. Several grocery stores can be found across the Keweenaw as well.
